  "body": "I have a bunch of contacts and also pending requests.\r\nIf I go to Settings -> Messaging -> Contacts, I get the tab view for these items.\r\n\r\nI've noticed that, when switching between contacts and pending items, the list of items \"jumps\" a bit as they seem to have different margins or something.\r\nIt's no big deal, just a tiny UI bug I assume. \r\n\r\nI tried capturing this in screenshots:\r\n![Screenshot from 2022-11-14 12-10-05](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/445106/201892359-e91d7ac7-23f4-483d-9434-4af249f83388.png)\r\n\r\nIt's hard to see like this, but the list of contacts is \"lower\" than the list of pending requests.\r\n![Screenshot from 2022-11-14 12-09-54](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/445106/201892371-628258cd-66f4-4235-8f26-8fde1c79c0bd.png)\r\n\r\n\r\n",
